{"tid":1427452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［歷史重演］ 2014 金紫荊 vs 2019 立法會 vs 2019 機場禁區","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:03:28.000Z","uid":287032,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86ba4937176436901fad7a1d85a6e8471871f7be","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"可能年輕既手足唔知<br />\n<br />\n2014年9月30日晚國慶前夕 網上有人建議佔領金紫荊，升起雨傘旗<br />\n之後有大量訊息出現：「唔好落中共面」、「要對準政權」、「會比藉口解放軍清場」、「邊個衝邊個就係鬼」<br />\n第二日仲出現人鏈守護金紫荊。<br />\n最後，國旗揚揚升起，拖延消耗策略成功，雨革步向衰亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLew3FX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLew3FX.jpg&h=cf0e82e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月1日下午兩點 第一批手足開始衝擊立法會，同樣地當日連登有8成人都唔支持， 「衝個班係鬼，係警方派人混入」、「佢地想減少七一和理非遊行人數」、「都無會開，比你衝到入去有咩用？」、「會比人告暴動坐十年監架」而一眾泛民議員亦以身相擋超過半個鐘，最後放棄。最後成功衝入，立法會被破壞，會議廳呢一張相成為全世界既頭條，震撼全球。但係各國多數領袖亦以不同意/譴責暴力作為聲明。<br />\n如果馬後炮黎講，會議廳正中央除左噴五大訴求之外，應該噴多四個英文字 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">H E L P</span></span><br />\n呢4個字其實相當震撼，代表左我地係受害者，我地已經無退路，我地請求你地救香港人！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WOYJM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WOYJM1.jpg&h=417a807f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e4utmyH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe4utmyH.jpg&h=ea7326a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場集會前夕<br />\n消息又滿天飛，「邊個衝一定係鬼，要拉住佢」、「入禁區係恐襲、會shoot to kill」、「比人拉、無得走、送頭」、「有人帶風向要衝，有中共黑警混入」，「比你地沖到入禁區又點？」咁就請你自己判斷佢地講得啱唔啱，你地係咪真係覺得佢地會開槍射殺幾千人？<br />\n<br />\n請大家一定堅守四大原則：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不督灰 不阻止 不分化</span></span><br />\n如果<span style=\"font-size: large;\">，如果</span>，最後真係大批人衝入去，請唔好破壞設施，應該再向全世界發出求救訊號，我地係受害者，我地無路可退。HELP!<br />\n或者其實大家諗定如果真衝左入去可以做啲乜， e.g. 宣言<br />\n<br />\n放核彈都唔割，何況衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個衝就割邊個請負皮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港加油<br />\n萬事小心</span>"},{"pid":"bc613676373e2205cb981745029b193e2e1e1f8f","tid":1427452,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"又話核彈都唔割既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6fbb26c0032d5c205574f75d01f2ea2ea76dab2","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc613676373e2205cb981745029b193e2e1e1f8f","tid":1427452,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"又話核彈都唔割既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"唔割！"},{"pid":"70d7111d28f5914cd2ab1b9eb95a4629e9d3b8ac","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb94d757240268a68fe4a7071df1461c4a69c9a1","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"694bdfb6bff3595cee8ba41e850f6e39a1d9ede4","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec507ed0cd5523805ac80bd43a96139efa47dba","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb0a3761815fa28112a1b3be2e1f4777f81a186","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d2914ef17bc18a4ef49106b04e8ef6e3cc856c","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ca34d43e9534ab8bb67daff2ea79385187c6789","tid":1427452,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike"